      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "1. Viewers can post comments on a Live video feed\n2. Viewers can see comments made before they joined the live feed\n3. Viewers can see new comments being posted while they are watching the live video",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Viewers can post comments on a Live video feed\n2. Viewers can see comments made before they joined the live feed\n3. Viewers can see new comments being posted while they are watching the live video",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 69
    },
